      "widgets_values": [
        "# 📌 ComfyUI Workflow Notes\n\n**Author:** Sharvin Suntoobacus  \n**YouTube Channel:** [CodeCraftersCorner](https://www.youtube.com/@CodeCraftersCorner)  \n**Patreon:** [Support on Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/codecrafterscorner)\n\n-----\n\n## ℹ️ About This Workflow\n\nThis workflow was created and shared by **Sharvin Suntoobacus** for the community.  \n**Main Model Card:** [Anima by Circlestone Labs](https://huggingface.co/circlestone-labs/Anima)\n\n-----\n\n## 🎥 Tutorial / Guide\n\nIf available, you can watch the video here:  \n[Watch on YouTube](https://www.google.com/search?q=PLACEHOLDER_VIDEO_LINK)  \n*Note: The link may take up to two days to update.*\n\n-----\n\n## 📥 Model Links (for Local Users)\n\n**diffusion\\_models**\n\n  - [anima-preview2.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/circlestone-labs/Anima/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/anima-preview2.safetensors?download=true)\n\n**text\\_encoders**\n\n  - [qwen\\_3\\_06b\\_base.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/circlestone-labs/Anima/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_06b_base.safetensors?download=true)\n\n**vae**\n\n  - [qwen\\_image\\_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/circlestone-labs/Anima/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors?download=true)\n\n-----\n\n## 📂 Model Storage Location\n\nPlace the downloaded files into the following directories within your ComfyUI installation:\n\n```text\n📂 ComfyUI/\n├── 📂 models/\n│   ├── 📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │   └── anima-preview2.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 text_encoders/\n│   │   └── qwen_3_06b_base.safetensors\n│   └── 📂 vae/\n│       └── qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n```\n\n-----\n\n## 💡 Notes\n\n  - **Update ComfyUI:** Ensure your ComfyUI is up to date to support these models.\n  - **Credit:** Please credit **Sharvin Suntoobacus** and share YouTube Channel **Code Crafters Corner** when sharing this workflow.\n  - **Support:** Your support on Patreon helps me continue creating these guides\\!\n\n-----\n\n🙏 Thank you for your support\\!\n"
